<h2 id="howto-use">HOWTO USE</h2>

<p>Just open the software -&gt; type the cation abbreviation &amp; inion abbreviation (I <strong>STRONGLY RECOMMEND</strong> selecting the auto completer to finish ionâ€™s abbreviation)-&gt; click <em>query</em> button.</p>

<h2 id="todo">TODO</h2>

<p>An un-completed API service was established on https://api.jonahliu.ga/. One can use GET method like <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">https://api.jonahliu.ga/?s=ILinfo.basic&amp;cid=c01001&amp;aid=a01001</code> obtaining a JSON-typed basic information. It is just the same as this software does.</p>

