<h2 id="if-you-are-an-expert">IF YOU ARE AN EXPERT</h2>

<p>You can find the original database-<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">ildb.db</code> in the source codes. It is a SQLite3 database, without additional encryption. You can get more detailed data about IL.</p>

